data.description: Introducing a Remarkable Renovation Opportunity! Unearth the hidden potential of this 1977 ranch-style home, nestled on an expansive just-under-1/3-acre lot. With a little vision, creativity, and some loving care, you can transform this diamond in the rough into your dream residence.Spacious Interior: Step inside and discover a roomy layout that's ready for your personal touch. The kitchen, complete with a charming dining nook, invites culinary creativity, while a formal dining area sets the stage for memorable gatherings. Cozy Fireplace: As the seasons change, gather around the large family room's inviting fireplace, providing warmth and ambiance on chilly evenings. Enjoy the luxury of two bedroom suites, each equipped with its own bathroom, offering unparalleled convenience and privacy for you and your guests. This property is a canvas waiting for your personal touch. With a bit of time and some elbow grease, you have the opportunity to restore and transform it into the beautiful home you've always envisioned. Don't miss this exceptional chance to reimagine and revitalize this 1977 ranch home. Bring your imagination, your dreams, and your passion for design to make this property your own. Seize the opportunity today, and turn this house into your dream home!
